keybind == C + Space 

Windows (tabs)

c  create window
w  list windows
n  next window
p  previous window
f  find window
,  name window
&  kill window

Panes (splits)

j  vertical split
l  horizontal split
o  swap panes
q  show pane numbers
x  kill pane
+  break pane into window (e.g. to select text by mouse to copy)
-  restore pane from window
⍽  space - toggle between layouts

Resize : Left, Right, Up, Down

__           
| |    __ _ _____   \ \   / (_)_ __ ___  
| |   / _` |_  / | | \ \ / /| | '_ ` _ \ 
| |__| (_| |/ /| |_| |\ V / | | | | | | |
|_____\__,_/___|\__, | \_/  |_|_| |_| |_|
                |___/

leader = space 

Buffers/ /Windows

<C-s>	 Save file
<S-h>	 Prev buffer
<S-l>	 Next buffer
<C-Left, Right, Up, Down> Resize 
<leader>`	Switch to Other Buffer
<leader>ww	Other window	
<leader>wd	Delete window

Tab 

<leader><tab><tab>	New Tab	
<leader><tab>]	Next Tab	
<leader><tab>d	Close Tab

Move 
<A-j>	Move down
<A-k>	Move up

<C-/>	Terminal


